    {
      "id": "BANNED_S23",
      "standard_name": "S-23",
      "aliases": [
        "s23",
        "S23 SARM",
        "S-23"
      ],
      "reason": "S-23 is a synthetic non-steroidal selective androgen receptor modulator (SARM) developed as an investigational male contraceptive candidate; it suppresses LH, FSH, and sperm production at moderate doses. It is not approved by any regulatory agency, not a dietary ingredient, and carries the same risks as other SARMs (endocrine suppression, hepatotoxicity). No NDI notification is on file. WADA prohibits it. Supplement products containing S-23 are adulterated with an unapproved compound whose contraceptive and androgenic effects are not declared on labels.",
