      "reason": "Adrafinil is a synthetic prodrug that metabolizes to modafinil in the body. Modafinil is a DEA Schedule IV controlled prescription drug (Provigil). By selling adrafinil as a supplement, manufacturers are effectively distributing an unapproved drug and bypassing Schedule IV controls. FDA has not approved adrafinil and has not accepted it as a dietary ingredient. WADA prohibits it in competition (stimulants class). Adrenal and cardiovascular effects mirror modafinil.",
