    {
      "id": "RECALLED_GE_LABS_YKARINE",
      "standard_name": "GE Labs Ykarine",
      "aliases": [
        "ge labs ykarine",
        "ykarine",
        "ge labs"
      ],
      "reason": "GE Labs Ykarine was found to contain undeclared trendione (trenbolone ketone / dione) — a designer anabolic steroid prohormone. The product was linked to a consumer stroke, which is a known risk of high-dose androgenic-anabolic steroids due to erythrocytosis, thrombosis, and dyslipidemia. Anabolic steroids are DEA Schedule III controlled substances when synthetic. The presence of undeclared trendione makes this product an adulterated, misbranded, and illegally marketed controlled substance analog.",
