      ],
      "reason": "Rheumacare Capsules were found to contain extreme lead contamination — up to 11,100 ppm (milligrams per kilogram) of lead — thousands of times above any acceptable level for a dietary supplement. Lead at this concentration causes acute and chronic lead poisoning: neurological damage, kidney injury, bone disruption, and in children severe developmental harm. California Prop 65's maximum level is 0.5 mcg/day total lead; a single capsule of this product would deliver a catastrophically toxic dose. FDA issued an urgent recall.",
