    {
      "id": "SPIKE_DEXAMETHASONE",
      "standard_name": "Dexamethasone",
      "aliases": [
        "decadron",
        "dexasone",
        "dexamethasone sodium phosphate",
        "dexamethasone"
      ],
      "reason": "Dexamethasone is a potent synthetic corticosteroid with approximately 25 times the anti-inflammatory potency of hydrocortisone. When found undeclared in supplements — typically in joint pain or immunity products — it suppresses the hypothalamic-pituitary-adrenal (HPA) axis without the user's knowledge. Abrupt cessation after chronic exposure can cause adrenal crisis. Long-term risks include Cushing's syndrome, osteoporosis, immunosuppression, and hyperglycemia. Its undeclared presence constitutes adulteration with a prescription drug.",
