      ],
      "reason": "Diclofenac is a prescription NSAID used for pain, arthritis, and inflammation. When found undeclared in dietary supplements — typically joint pain or anti-inflammatory products — it exposes users to serious risks without medical supervision: gastrointestinal bleeding, renal impairment, and elevated cardiovascular risk (heart attack, stroke). FDA has warned that undeclared NSAIDs in supplements are a recurring adulterant pattern in products marketed for pain and inflammation. Users on blood thinners or with kidney disease face life-threatening risk.",
