      ],
      "reason": "Muscimol is the primary psychoactive compound in Amanita muscaria mushrooms. It is a potent GABA-A receptor agonist causing sedation, euphoria, altered perception, and at higher doses: seizures, loss of consciousness, and respiratory depression. The margin between psychoactive and toxic doses is narrow and highly variable. Muscimol itself (as isolated compound or concentrated extract) has been marketed in gummies and capsules, leading to the 2024 Diamond Shruumz mass poisoning event.",
